---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base
  title="Thank you"
  description="Thanks for telling Jonathan what's next for your assistant. He reads every note and follows up personally."
  noindex
>
  <div class="container next-page">
    <div class="book-hero panel">
      <p class="book-kicker">Got it</p>
      <h1>Thank you</h1>

      <p class="book-sub">
        I read every one of these myself, and I'll follow up at the email you
        left. In the meantime, keep the assistant running. A brief every
        morning for a week is where it starts to compound.
      </p>

      <p class="book-reassure">
        The full setup guide lives at <a href="/ai-assistant/cowork/">builtwithjon.com/ai-assistant/cowork/</a> whenever you need it.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Base>
